summary: A nice little hideout to relax in.
descriptionHtml:
A hideout what gives you a alchemy table and an enchanting table also a tanning rack. But inside youll find a bed a nice fireplace to sit by and your own chest next to the chest there is a two weapon racks.

This house is great if you just want to relax. The house is located just outside riverwood it will be on your map so you dont need to go searching.
author: oOVenomOo
